      <p>Analogously, OpenAnnotate annotates narrow/broad peak openness for ENCODE samples and ATACdb peak openness for ATACdb samples with the average number of peaks overlapping with the given region of size <inline-formula><tex-math id="M8">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
